cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use TRACE in your work, please cite as below."
type: software
title: "TRACE: Timestamped Record of Agentic Chain Execution"
abstract: >
  TRACE is an append-only execution record for the REACH + OCTO ecosystem.
  Where REACH reaches and OCTO orchestrates, TRACE remembers — every arm,
  every chain, every human decision, every artifact, every failure. A flat
  NDJSON file and a five-tool MCP server are all that is required.
  No database. No dashboard. No always-on process.
authors:
